{"tid":1931461,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★ 姆紐欽：美國失業率恐飆至20%！","createTime":"2020-03-18T07:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T07:11:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"26661cc0b41bdc918dd74efc79db5615996c4977","tid":1931461,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒引述消息報道，美國財長姆紐欽在提交規模高達1萬億美元(約7.8萬億港元)以上的經濟刺激計劃的同時，警告共和黨參議員，如果政府不採取行動，新冠肺炎疫情大流行可能會使美國失業率飆升至20%。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，姆紐欽認為新冠肺炎疫情蔓延，對經濟產生的影響可能會比2008年的金融危機還要大。如果議員不立即為工人和中小企業提供財務支持的話，超高的失業率便會成為一種可能。<br />\n不過，財政部發言人Monica Crowley透露，「今天與共和黨參議員舉行會議時，姆紐欽為了說明的目，用了幾個數學例子，但他絕非暗指情況會是如此，」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，20%的失業率將是美國大蕭條時期的兩倍，是美國自大蕭條以來的最高失業率。如果失業率達到20%，根據目前的美國勞動力，意味着將有超過3,200萬美國人失業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200318/bkn-20200318072750067-0318_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200318%2Fbkn-20200318072750067-0318_00842_001.html&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=f5b0bb87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200318/bkn-20200318072750067-0318_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f7571775cb0ea706d339201e54618283f4556790","tid":1931461,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c834917494e52a551f5d11c95a17696c2fee2b3","tid":1931461,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:26:20.000Z","msg":"To make America Poor again<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /